<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />

    <title>Housing Levy Calculator Kenya | Calculate Housing Levy Online</title>

    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Free Kenya Housing Levy Calculator. Calculate your Affordable Housing Levy contribution instantly using the latest Kenya Housing Levy rate. Fast, accurate, and easy to use."
    />

    <meta
      name="keywords"
      content="Housing Levy Calculator Kenya, Kenya Housing Levy Calculator, Affordable Housing Levy Calculator, Housing Levy contribution calculator, Kenya payroll calculator"
    />

    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

    <link
      rel="canonical"
      href="https://yourdomain.com/housing-levy-calculator"
    />

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
  </head>

  <body data-api-url="<%= API_URL %>">
    <%- include('../shared/header') %>

    <main>
      <section>
        <h1>Housing Levy Calculator Kenya</h1>

        <p>
          As an employee, your employer will deduct this tax and remit it to KRA
          on your behalf through KRA Online Portal. Housing Levy is a mandatory
          statutory deduction in Kenya introduced to support the Affordable
          Housing Programme. It is charged as a fixed percentage of an
          employee’s gross income, with a matching employer contribution, making
          it a shared responsibility between employer and employee. The levy is
          deducted monthly and remitted to the government to fund the
          development of affordable housing units and related social
          infrastructure. Contributors may benefit through access to affordable
          home ownership or rental options, and in some cases, refunds or
          credits if they do not ultimately receive a housing allocation.
        </p>

        <h2>Housing Levy Rates Effective (Current Kenya Rates)</h2>

        <table>
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Employee Contribution</th>
              <th>Employer Contribution</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>

          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td>1.5% of Gross Pay</td>
              <td>1.5% of Gross Pay</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </section>

      <section id="housing-levy-form-section">
        <form id="housing-levy-form" autocomplete="off">
          <h2>Housing Levy Calculator</h2>

          <div>
            <label for="gross-pay">Gross Monthly Salary (KES)</label>
            <input
              id="gross-pay"
              name="grossPay"
              type="number"
              placeholder="0.00"
              min="0"
              step="0.01"
              required
            />
          </div>

          <p id="error-message" hidden></p>

          <button type="submit">Calculate</button>
        </form>
      </section>

      <section id="results" hidden aria-live="polite">
        <div class="results-success">
          <p id="success-message"></p>
        </div>

        <h2>Results</h2>

        <table>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td>Gross Salary</td>
              <td id="gross-salary">KES 0.00</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Housing Levy</strong></td>
              <td id="housing-levy"><strong>KES 0.00</strong></td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>

        <button id="reset-btn">Reset</button>
      </section>
    </main>

    <%- include('../shared/footer') %>

    <script src="/js/housingLevy.js" defer></script>
  </body>
</html>
